name: stomach earrings in gold leaf
description:
Mexican milagros, Chinese medicine, and the beauty of human anatomy
is the inspiration behind these stomach earrings. 
They were designed by Kristin Abhalter on a computer and printed with a 3D printer in a sandstone composite material. 
They are sealed with varnish and available in white finish or gold leaf which is applied by hand. 
The french earrings hooks are sterling silver.
